118
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,400
Yeah, I heard about it too.

119
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,740
You didn't hear the English listening section?

120
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:30,280
Yes.

121
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,440
Keep your voice down.

122
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,900
I don't want to hold a press conference here.

123
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,159
Someone messed with you!

124
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,360
Keep your voice down!

125
00:07:37,810 --> 00:07:38,640
Anyway,

126
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:41,200
