I told him that they beat you this morning,

281
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,320
and he was shocked.

282
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:16,920
Hey, I'll send you another picture.

283
00:15:18,570 --> 00:15:19,830
See?

284
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:23,000
This is called divine justice, the heavens are watching,

285
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,710
and justice prevails.

286
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:37,410
Take care of Wang.

287
00:15:37,410 --> 00:15:38,040
No need.

288
00:15:43,090 --> 00:15:44,570
Is Tian back?

289
00:15:44,570 --> 00:15:45,600
I'll talk to you later.

290
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,520
Tian's here.

291
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:55,570
What?

292
00:15:56,450 --> 00:15:58,740
The two hooligans who beat me today were caught.

293
00:15:58,740 --> 00:15:59,560
Do you know?

294
00:16:03,190 --> 00:16:03,890
Yes.

295
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:07,900
Gao Tianyang showed me the live stream.

296
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:17,610
Was it you?

297
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:19,080
What do you mean?

298
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:26,550
It was captured on the security camera.

299
00:16:26,690 --> 00:16:27,820
Your shoes.

300
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,710
Impossible.

301
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:30,640
Impossible?

302
00:16:58,730 --> 00:17:00,190
I was so far away.

303
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:07,579
Yes.

304
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,470
It was me.

305
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:15,060
Tian, you're back?

306
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:15,829
Yes!

307
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:17,280
Wash your hands and clean up.

308
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:18,670
We'll eat soon.

309
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:19,710
Okay.

310
00:17:29,930 --> 00:17:32,540
This afternoon, I went to Joy to buy some water

311
00:17:34,130 --> 00:17:36,460
and happened to see two security cameras.

312
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,950
The owner of Joy must have installed them

313
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:42,620
because he was concerned about thieves at night.

314
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:45,420
So, I downloaded the footage and sent it to Zhao Xi.

315
00:17:46,150 --> 00:17:49,480
I figured that with so many people coming and going in the store,

316
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,540
there might be a chance to catch them.

317
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:55,840
But I didn't mention that you got beaten.

318
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:57,760
It was a coincidence

319
00:17:58,190 --> 00:18:00,790
that those two hooligans were causing a scene.

320
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:10,420
Would you have told me

321
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:12,750
if I hadn't found out?

322
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:21,510
Do you just enjoy doing good deeds?

323
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:24,680
Would you have kept quiet if I hadn't asked?

324
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:33,090
I was just thinking

325
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:38,240
that you must have been very scared at that time,

326
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:41,960
really hoping someone could help you,

327
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,090
but there was no one.

328
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,950
There was no one there

329
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,940
but yourself,

330
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:53,060
two hooligans out of nowhere,

331
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:57,390
and the fear of not knowing whether you could win.

332
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:03,610
If I were you,

333
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:06,250
I would probably have been panicking too.

334
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:17,730
I didn't know about it at the time, so I couldn't help you...

335
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:20,620
but I didn't want to do nothing at all.

336
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,640
Better late than never.

337
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:40,810
It's not a big deal. Don't worry.

338
00:19:46,630 --> 00:19:47,330
What?

339
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:51,600
Well,

340
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:58,330
I twisted my leg

341
00:19:58,350 --> 00:20:00,010
while fighting this morning.

342
00:20:01,210 --> 00:20:02,580
Carry me upstairs.

343
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,230
Go upstairs.

344
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:38,080
Don't let my dad or your mom see.

345
00:20:50,840 --> 00:20:53,570
Why are you going upstairs? It's time to eat!

346
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,450
We're here.

347
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:16,400
Thank you.

348
00:21:22,690 --> 00:21:24,090
Aren't you getting down?

349
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:26,110
Well,

350
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:28,200
help me all the way

351
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:30,080
and take me to the door.

352
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:41,100
Open the door for me.

353
00:21:56,910 --> 00:21:58,530
Thanks again.

354
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:02,130
You should skip dinner.

355
00:22:02,490 --> 00:22:03,140
Why?

356
00:22:03,860 --> 00:22:05,190
You need to lose weight.

357
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:08,100
I take back my thanks.

358
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:10,840
Hey, wait a minute.

359
00:22:13,120 --> 00:22:14,120
Give me your hand.

360
00:22:21,450 --> 00:22:22,850
Don't get too emotional.

361
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:25,260
You gave this to me this morning.

362
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:26,610
There's one piece left.

363
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:44,870
Does it hurt?

364
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:53,160
I can be pretty careless.

365
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,690
If it does hurt, let me know.

366
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,590
Okay.

367
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:12,490
Thank you.

368
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:15,540
Oh, right.

369
00:23:16,340 --> 00:23:19,190
Did you beat them up for me today?

370
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:28,920
No.

371
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:34,280
When they tried to run away, they happened to pass right in front of me,

372
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:36,010
so I just blocked them a little.

373
00:23:40,210 --> 00:23:42,910
Well, he hit me 6 times today.

374
00:23:43,050 --> 00:23:44,450
Did you block him 6 times?

375
00:23:49,370 --> 00:23:51,060
Definitely more than 6 times.

376
00:23:56,770 --> 00:24:00,400
You two can come down for dinner now!

377
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:02,380
I'm not eating today.

378
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:05,250
I'm on a diet.

379
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,240
This guy

380
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:39,200
must have gone back to bed for a nap.

381
00:26:07,670 --> 00:26:10,450
I'll send the samples to you as soon as I get them tomorrow.

382
00:26:10,450 --> 00:26:11,040
Yes.

383
00:26:14,730 --> 00:26:15,410
Okay.

384
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,580
Everything was made as we discussed before.

385
00:26:17,580 --> 00:26:18,310
Don't worry.

386
00:26:18,670 --> 00:26:19,370
Okay, bye.

387
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,050
Time to eat.

388
00:26:20,050 --> 00:26:20,670
Okay.

389
00:26:21,670 --> 00:26:22,280
Let me help you.

390
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,210
Thank you.

391
00:26:23,970 --> 00:26:25,760
Morning, Wang.

392
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:26,660
Morning.

393
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:27,730
Come on.

394
00:26:28,190 --> 00:26:29,190
Sit here.

395
00:26:29,230 --> 00:26:31,630
You're finally willing to come down to eat.

396
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,480
Wang,

397
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:37,020
didn't you say you want to eat Shaomai?

398
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:39,910
I specifically learned how to make Shaomai online.

399
00:26:39,910 --> 00:26:40,780
Have a try.

400
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:43,800
If you like it, I'll make it for you again in the future.

401
00:26:44,390 --> 00:26:45,040
Oh.

402
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:52,590
Where is Jiang Tian?

403
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:54,650
Oh, he went to the Little White House.

404
00:26:54,910 --> 00:26:55,750
Oh.

405
00:26:56,250 --> 00:26:59,030
Aren't you two going to the English competition today?

406
00:26:59,030 --> 00:26:59,760
Yes.

407
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,250
It's this afternoon.

408
00:27:01,250 --> 00:27:02,080
I'll go later.

409
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:02,920
Good luck.

410
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:04,360
Eat more.

411
00:27:09,620 --> 00:27:10,970
Yeah, I don't know what's wrong.

412
00:27:10,970 --> 00:27:12,700
It just isn't cooling anymore.

413
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,330
There's no problem.

414
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,430
There's no problem?

415
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:21,960
But why isn't it cooling?

416
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:24,070
Did you accidentally adjust the temperature?

417
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,150
I didn't adjust the temperature.

418
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:28,820
But sometimes the engine makes this noise,

419
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,100
then it stops for a bit,

420
00:27:30,150 --> 00:27:32,950
and then it makes the same noise again. It sounds weird.

421
00:27:32,950 --> 00:27:34,750
Alright, I've adjusted it back.

422
00:27:35,990 --> 00:27:36,790
It's fine now?

423
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,760
It will gradually get cold.

424
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,410
Let me know if there are any more problems.

425
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:44,050
Okay.

426
00:27:47,580 --> 00:27:48,580
I'm leaving then.

427
00:27:48,910 --> 00:27:50,000
Hey, wait.

428
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:53,200
Where are you going in such a hurry? You haven't eaten yet.

429
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:54,430
I have an English competition this afternoon.

430
00:27:54,430 --> 00:27:56,280
I have an appointment with someone to take the subway together.

431
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:57,370
You have an appointment with someone?

432
00:27:57,370 --> 00:27:58,040
Yes.

433
00:27:58,060 --> 00:27:58,850
Who?

434
00:28:01,370 --> 00:28:03,430
The person who freeloaded last time.

435
00:28:04,410 --> 00:28:05,230
Wang?

436
00:28:05,430 --> 00:28:05,980
Yes.

437
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,850
How could you say he was a freeloader?

438
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:09,430
He's so well-behaved,

439
00:28:09,460 --> 00:28:11,940
polite, and not cold like you.

440
00:28:12,850 --> 00:28:14,890
He hasn't come here to eat for a while.

441
00:28:14,890 --> 00:28:17,430
Does he not like my cooking?

442
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:21,130
No, he actually thinks the school's food is worse than yours.

443
00:28:22,090 --> 00:28:23,390
So, does that mean

444
00:28:23,410 --> 00:28:26,240
he likes my cooking?

445
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:28,200
Then why didn't he come today?

446
00:28:28,450 --> 00:28:29,390
Did you invite him?

447
00:28:29,390 --> 00:28:29,970
I...

448
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:33,000
I didn't invite him. But you didn't invite him either?

449
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,870
How did you make friends with him?

450
00:28:34,980 --> 00:28:36,040
Give me your phone.

451
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,040
What are you doing?

452
00:28:37,040 --> 00:28:39,300
Give it to me. Hurry up. No more nonsense.

453
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:43,380
Wang. Wang.

454
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:47,860
Wang.

455
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:51,400
Wang,

456
00:28:51,450 --> 00:28:53,850
Jiang Tian asked you to come over for lunch.

457
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:54,930
Okay. Hurry up.

458
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:56,670
Alright.

459
00:28:57,140 --> 00:28:58,360
I'll go cook now.

460
00:28:58,770 --> 00:29:00,690
By the way, there's a bit of a leak in the toilet.

461
00:29:00,690 --> 00:29:02,410
Could you take a look?

462
00:29:03,610 --> 00:29:05,140
What happened to your hand?

463
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,780
It's just a scratch.

464
00:29:08,190 --> 00:29:09,320
I'll take care of it.

465
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:19,800
Hey, Wang, come.

466
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:20,810
Let's eat.

467
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:22,120
Hurry up and eat.

468
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:25,050
Where is Jiang Tian?

469
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,890
My house is old.

470
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,810
The toilet and the pipes are leaking.

471
00:29:28,810 --> 00:29:30,610
I asked him to check it out for me.

472
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:31,700
Oh.

473
00:29:32,430 --> 00:29:33,180
Eat up.

474
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:36,380
So, he invited me over today

475
00:29:36,410 --> 00:29:37,620
just for lunch,

476
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:40,100
or can I come here to eat in the future as well?

477
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:43,340
Actually, it was my invitation.

478
00:29:45,530 --> 00:29:46,240
Oh.

479
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:47,740
Well...

480
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:49,440
Today's...

481
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:51,080
You first.

482
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:53,180
Well...

483
00:29:54,120 --> 00:29:56,190
Did Tian get into a fight?

484
00:29:58,990 --> 00:30:00,820
I noticed he had a band-aid

485
00:30:00,990 --> 00:30:02,430
on his hand today.

486
00:30:02,970 --> 00:30:05,570
He said it was just a minor scratch by accident.

487
00:30:06,610 --> 00:30:08,170
Even if I ask him,

488
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:10,310
he won't tell me the truth.

489
00:30:13,850 --> 00:30:16,570
So, did you invite me over today

490
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,980
just to ask about this?

491
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:22,780
Honestly,

492
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:25,560
I've never seen Tian be this close

493
00:30:25,610 --> 00:30:27,160
to anyone before,

494
00:30:28,410 --> 00:30:29,340
including me.

495
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:35,460
He's always been reluctant to interact with others,

496
00:30:36,950 --> 00:30:38,110
so,

497
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,940
he's very cautious

498
00:30:40,650 --> 00:30:42,450
and doesn't want to hurt anyone.

499
00:30:43,610 --> 00:30:45,740
Maybe because he's been hurt himself,

500
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:49,270
he particularly understands other people's wounds

501
00:30:49,290 --> 00:30:50,790
and needs.

502
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:54,560
You know,

503
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:58,280
he's like a martial arts master in those martial arts films—

504
00:30:58,300 --> 00:31:00,030
if someone gets within three feet of him,

505
00:31:00,030 --> 00:31:02,740
they'd be knocked away by his protective aura.

506
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:06,440
He's been on his own since he was young.

507
00:31:06,710 --> 00:31:09,310
His grandmother and parents have ignored him,

508
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:12,450
so he isolated himself from them.

509
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:15,610
No one can see

510
00:31:15,950 --> 00:31:18,230
what's going on in his mind.

511
00:31:18,860 --> 00:31:20,660
He doesn't let anyone get close,

512
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:21,990
so,

513
00:31:22,490 --> 00:31:24,870
no one can enter his inner world.

514
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:28,990
You're

515
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:30,810
the first friend I've seen him

516
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:33,710
bring over here.

517
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,440
So, I want to ask you

518
00:31:36,930 --> 00:31:39,070
for a favor:

519
00:31:40,080 --> 00:31:41,810
don't let him push you away.

520
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:46,100
I hope you can get closer to him, okay?

521
00:32:23,500 --> 00:32:25,850
[Qi Jiahao]

522
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:29,570
How to buy this?

523
00:32:29,570 --> 00:32:32,000
There are so many stations; where do I need to go from and to?

524
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,690
Use this.

525
00:32:36,150 --> 00:32:38,480
I guess you don't have an EasyCard, right?

526
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:39,700
Here.

527
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:41,630
Oh.

528
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,480
How much do I own you?

529
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:45,310
It's okay.

530
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:48,500
As long as you do well in the English competition.

531
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:51,070
Even if you don't come in first,

532
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:52,670
at least aim for the top five.

533
00:32:56,280 --> 00:32:58,860
Okay, I'll keep it with me during the exam

534
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,540
and carry it with me usually,

535
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:02,270
like an amulet. Okay?

536
00:33:02,670 --> 00:33:04,110
Can you be more dramatic?

537
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:07,150
[Wang]

538
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,240
Let's go.

539
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:08,890
Okay.

540
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:16,490
Everyone, remember what I said:

541
00:33:16,530 --> 00:33:18,840
aim for victory from stability and score from risks.

542
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:20,420
Write down what you know first

543
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:22,130
to secure your base score.

544
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,120
For what you don't know…

545
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:25,240
Why are you two so late?

546
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,450
I'll say it again.

547
00:33:26,450 --> 00:33:27,910
You two listen carefully.

548
00:33:27,990 --> 00:33:30,640
Write down what you know first to secure your base score,

549
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,280
and leave what you don't know until the end.

550
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:34,130
If you have time, make sure to attempt them as well.

551
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:36,420
Check your answers several times

552
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:37,850
and don't hand the paper in early.

553
00:33:37,850 --> 00:33:40,150
I've emphasized this many times already.

554
00:33:40,150 --> 00:33:41,790
Don't hand the paper in early.

555
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:43,790
The exam is about to start.

556
00:33:43,830 --> 00:33:44,830
Get ready to go in.

557
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:46,480
I'll help you both check in.

558
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,460
Thank you.

559
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:50,330
Thank you.

560
00:33:51,870 --> 00:33:53,410
Hey, I just called you.

561
00:33:53,410 --> 00:33:54,670
Why didn't you answer?

562
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:56,280
Oh, sorry about that.

563
00:33:56,970 --> 00:33:57,810
What's wrong?

564
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:01,710
